key-generic_valve_key.name: CS:GO Case Key
key-generic_valve_key.description: This key will open any Valve Series Weapon Case. Non-Valve Series cases (e.g. eSports Case) require their own key to open.

key-1204.name: eSports Key
key-1204.description: This key opens any eSports Case.\n\nA portion of the proceeds from the sale of this key will go towards one of the established community-run CS:GO tournaments. Stay tuned for further announcements.

key-1212.name: CS:GO Capsule Key
key-1212.description: This key will open any Valve Series Capsule.
